window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>War is but an Opportunity</b></p> <p>After experiencing death and an irreversible transformation, Adelheid must juggle between hiding her new inhuman nature with her wish to become the next ruler of the Vuldar Empire. Her greatest rival for the throne, William von Vuldar, has already joined the battlefield, but she has to play catch up. She must use all resources and grab every opportunity to join the war and rise above.</p> <p>However, only those in war will learn that everything has a cost.</p>"; 
